OL,3,CScottish Borders receives Scotland's
OL,4,Cfirst drone medical delivery
OL,6,FFor the first time drones are being
OL,7,Fused to deliver laboratory samples
OL,8,Fbetween NHS Scotland health boards,
OL,9,Ftaking as little as 35 minutes.
OL,11,FMelrose was the first location to
OL,12,Freceive a medical drone delivery in
OL,13,FScotland, travelling from Edinburgh, a
OL,14,Fdelivery service which could take up
OL,15,Fto five hours on the road.
OL,17,FThe #7m UK Government project, named
OL,18,FProject CAELUS, aims to be a
OL,19,Fpioneering move in how medical
OL,20,Fsupplies are sent to remote locations
OL,21,Facross Scotland.
