OL,3,CScottish Borders receives Scotland's
OL,4,Cfirst drone medical delivery
OL,6,FMike Kane, Minister for Aviation and
OL,7,FMaritime, claims it could be a
OL,8,F"technological revolution".
OL,10,F"I want to help all players in the
OL,11,Findustry across the country to embrace
OL,12,Fthese innovative solutions that
OL,13,Fenhance regional connectivity and pave
OL,14,Fthe way for a more sustainable future."
OL,16,FAberdeen International Airport has led
OL,17,Fthe drone trials across Scotland. Andy
OL,18,FCliffe, CEO of AGS Airports, says
OL,19,FProject CAELUS can benefit health
OL,20,Fservices across Scotland.
