OL,3,CScottish Borders receives Scotland's
OL,4,Cfirst drone medical delivery
OL,6,FHe said: "It can mobilise and drive
OL,7,Fchange for the better. Fostering
OL,8,Finnovation is one of the ways we can
OL,9,Fachieve this and through Project
OL,10,FCAELUS we have a real opportunity to
OL,11,Frevolutionise the way in which
OL,12,Fhealthcare services are delivered
OL,13,Facross Scotland."
OL,15,FNHS bosses say the use of drones could
OL,16,Fallow for same day diagnosis and
OL,17,Ftreatment.
OL,19,FThe trial will now continue before the
OL,20,Ffindings are presented to the NHS and
OL,21,Fthe government.
